  • Package net.kencochrane.raven.event

    • Class net.kencochrane.raven.event.Event extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • id

          UUID id
          Unique identifier of the event.

        • message

          String message
          User-readable representation of this event.

        • timestamp

          Date timestamp
          Exact time when the logging occurred.

        • level

          Event.Level level
          The record severity.

        • logger

          String logger
          The name of the logger which created the record.

        • platform

          String platform
          A string representing the currently used platform (java/python).

        • culprit

          String culprit
          Function call which was the primary perpetrator of this event.

        • tags

          Map<K,V> tags
          A map or list of tags for this event.

          Automatically created with a Map that is made unmodifiable by the EventBuilder.

        • serverName

          String serverName
          Identifies the host client from which the event was recorded.

        • extra

          Map<K,V> extra
          A map or list of additional properties for this event.

          Automatically created with a Map that is made unmodifiable by the EventBuilder.

        • checksum

          String checksum
          Checksum for the event, allowing to group events with a similar checksum.

        • sentryInterfaces

          Map<K,V> sentryInterfaces
          Additional interfaces for other information and metadata.

          Automatically created with a Map that is made unmodifiable by the EventBuilder.
